title: Evil Dead PSP Prx collection
description:
The Semi-Complete Evil Dead (1&2) and Army of Darkness Opening-plugin.prx collection.

I tried to get the best quality files that I could find, but you know the first Evil Dead is real old now, and the audio just sucks on it.

In each folder is a .wav file for your listening pleasures to help you decide which one to use.
